

First make sure Leiningen is installed:

$ cd ~/bin
$ wget http://github.com/technomancy/leiningen/raw/stable/bin/lein
$ chmod +x lein
$ lein self-install

Then download and install the project dependencies:

$ lein deps

Compile it:

$ lein compile

And create a uberjar that contains all of the project files and dependencies:

$ lein uberjar

And finally, run incanter-helloworld:

$ java -jar incanter-helloworld-standalone.jar

